snippet: The police say a man who led the authorities on a chase in Nevada and Utah is a former Nascar driver.
abstract: Police arrest Nascar driver Timothy Tyler Andrew Walker in Utah following interstate chase; Walker is found in possession of marijuana, pills and open containers of alcohol.
lead_paragraph: The police say a man who led the authorities on a chase in Nevada and Utah is a former Nascar driver.

headline.seo: Racer Timothy Tyler Andrew Walker Is Said to Have Led Police on Chase
headline.main: Former Nascar Driver Leads Police on Chase
